- System SHALL support event deduplication based on event IDs

### FR2: Real-time Event Processing
- System SHALL process events in real-time as they arrive
- System SHALL route events to appropriate downstream processors
- System SHALL support event transformation and enrichment
- System SHALL handle event processing failures with retry logic
```

